title 0.6: New note

note over browser:
when the button on the form is clicked
browser starts executing js-code
end note

note over browser:
creates a new note
adds it to the notes list
end note

note over browser:
renders notes to display
and sends the new note to the server
end note

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over server:
server creates a new note object
and adds it to an array called notes
end note

server->browser: responds with status code 201 created
